<br>
he dropped like a rock, we sent in the chanter to eat the first DT.  Then he DTed me ... Then the SK FDed the DT onto the monk (which was hella funny).  Then the Necro Lifeburned and owned him.<br>
<br>
Hes a short fast fight, if youve got DPS, you wont have a prob.<br>
<br>
Have a Chanter take the DT, they dont do much damage compared to the rest of the classes, then go all out offensive, Fellstrike or aggressive, dont worry bout aggro control, just hit him with everything you got as fast as possible.  LB Necros, and MB wizards are good people to have for this, as well as mages and druids, as they got them summoned only nukes.  Even the cleric should be nuking unless you need a spot heal.  he doesnt hit too hard, maybe 140s or so ... so healing should be minimal.<br>
<br>
Just remember, HARD FAST DAMAGE. and youll be fine with a single group.  If your feeling unsure, take 2 down. <p>Master Xith N'Shezbenon<br>
